d  (2021):[6] "Product Information. Slynd (drospirenone)." Duchesnay Inc  (2021):[7] "Product Information. Evotaz (atazanavir-cobicistat)." Bristol-Myers Squibb  (2022):[8] "Product Information. Evotaz (atazanavir-cobicistat)." Bristol-Myers Squibb Australia Pty Ltd  (2023):[9] "Product Information. Evotaz (atazanavir-cobicistat)." Bristol-Myers Squibb Pharmaceuticals Ltd  (2021):', 1767363028);
